name: Jeanette Johnson
description: I consider myself to be a great friend and believe I should be dating one in kind. Family and friends are the most important components of my happiness. I truly enjoy making people in my life happy but crave reciprocation. I take great care of people I love, and would especially care for a person who is reciprocally loving and attentive to me. My goals are to enjoy the rest of my life; work as long as I can or for as long as I need to, learn all I can, give back as often as I can, and do as many of the things that I/my partner enjoy as possible!
